title: Various Artists - Navigatorz Fresh!! Indie Playlist March 2012
description:
Welcome to Third edition for this year, of NAVIGATORZ FRESH!! Indie playlists...We want to announce that 2012., you can expect more suprises from us. You'll be able to download much more special NAVIGATORZ playlists. 
Anyone who is interested in sending your own stuff (via links to downloads), we would gladly listen to your music and include it in our list or radio show if we find it good, so more people would hear it...This month artwork is from Mia Matovic. 
From this month Navigatorz Radio show running again. You can listen NEW!! FRESH!! indie singles every MONDAY @ www.navigatorzfm.listen2myradio.com from 8PM CET.

Best regards

Navigatorz team

P.S. of course, if you like the music, support the artists and buy their music!

NAVIGATOR, music team producing beats,grooves and much more...And an awesome DJ team and a soundsystem as well proudly presents:

NAVIGATORZ FRESH!! INDIE PLAYLIST MARCH 2012

NAVIGATORZ FRESH!! INDIE PLAYLIST contains the team's choice when it comes to independent music acts,ranging from guitar, electronic,acts to so called "indietronica" and experimental sounds...

Enjoy!
